                <head>190. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>Between January 30 and February 8, Saudi Arabian King <persName corresp="#p_SAA1"
                        >Saud</persName> and other Saudi dignitaries visited Washington and held
                    extensive discussions with President <persName corresp="#p_EDD1"
                        >Eisenhower</persName>, Secretary <persName corresp="#p_DJF1"
                        >Dulles</persName>, and other high-ranking United States officials. For
                    documentation on the visit of King <persName corresp="#p_SAA1">Saud</persName>,
                    including information relating to the Baghdad Pact and other regional issues,
                    see <ref target="frus1955-57v13#pg_413">volume XIII, pages 413</ref> ff.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
